data.description: 🏡JOIN US Sunday, 2/4 from 2-4PM🏡 • Seller Offering $10,000 BUYER CREDIT for updates • Welcome to this charming 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath end-unit condo/townhouse at 411 Hampton Ct in Falls Church City • Hardwood floors & fresh paint throughout • The renovated gourmet kitchen with granite counters is sure to be a delight for any home chef • RARE Fireplace in the living room is perfect for those cold winter evenings • The outdoor space with native plantings adds a lovely touch, creating a serene and natural atmosphere • If you're seeking a place that combines modern updates with a cozy ambiance and convenience, this property checks those boxes • The bustling surroundings and accessibility to everyday necessities  truly make this a delightful place to call home • Minutes to downtown shops, restaurants, grocery stores, parks, and convenient access to commuter routes and public transportation, including Metro Rail and Bus • Seize the opportunity to live in the heart of "The Little City" in highly sought after Winter Hill •  Love Where You Live - Welcome Home!
